Package model

Class Records

java.lang.Object
model.Records
Direct Known Subclasses:
Appointment, MedicalRecord, PaymentRecord
public abstract class Records extends Object
Abstract class representing a generic record in the Hospital Management System (HMS). This class contains common fields such as record ID, creation date, update date, and status for all types of records in the system.
